### ============================================================================
### ADMIN → ROLES — /api/v1/admin/roles
### ============================================================================

### List roles
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get role by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/roles/{{roleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Create role
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "COMPANY_ADMIN",
  "description": "Company administrator role"
}

### Update role
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/roles/{{roleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "COMPANY_ADMIN",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### Delete role
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/roles/{{roleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
